  "Quadratic": "二次二次曲线",
  "A geometric sequence has the same structure as an exponential function: each term is multiplied by a constant factor. The explicit formula a(n) = a(1) · r^(n−1) mirrors y = a · bˣ.": "几何序列的结构与指数函数的结构相同:每个术语乘以一个不变系数。明确的公式a(n)=a(1) / r(n-1)反射y = a / bx。",
  "What is a geometric sequence?": "什么是几何序列?",
  "A sequence where each term is found by adding a constant to the previous term": "通过在前一术语中添加一个常数来查找每个术语的序列",
  "A sequence of perfect squares": "完美的方形序列",
  "Any sequence of numbers that increases": "任何增加的序列数",
  "A sequence where each term is found by multiplying the previous term by a constant ratio": "将上一个术语乘以恒定比率,从而找到每个术语的序列",
  "A geometric sequence is a sequence in which each term after the first is found by multiplying the previous term by a fixed nonzero number called the common ratio. This is in contrast to an arithmetic sequence, which uses addition.": "几何序列是一个序列,其中第一个术语之后的每个术语通过将上一个术语乘以一个固定的非零数字(称为通用比率)而发现。这与使用加法的算术序列形成对照。",
  "What is the common ratio in a geometric sequence?": "几何序列中的常见比率是什么?",
  "The average of all terms": "所有任期的平均数",
  "The constant factor r found by dividing any term by the previous term": "常数 r , 将任何任期除以前一任期时发现的常数 r",
  "The difference between consecutive terms": "连续任期之间的差额",
  "The sum of the first and last terms": "第一次和最后一次任期之和和",
  "The common ratio r is the constant multiplier between successive terms. It is found by dividing any term by its predecessor: r = a(n+1)/a(n). If this ratio is the same for all pairs, the sequence is geometric.": "共同比率 r 是连续两个任期之间的恒定乘数。 其前身为 r = a(n+1)/ a(n) , 通过将其任何任期除以 r = a(n+1)/ a(n) 来发现。 如果该比率对所有配对都相同, 则序列为几何。",
  "What is an explicit formula?": "什么是明确的公式?",
  "A formula for the sum of all terms": "所有条件之和的公式",
  "A formula that gives the next term based on the previous term": "以上一任期为基础给下一个任期的公式",
  "A formula that only works for the first term": "只适用于第一个任期的公式",
  "A formula that directly calculates any term's value based on its position number n": "一种公式,该公式根据其位置号 n 直接计算任何条件值",
  "An explicit formula lets you find any term directly from its position number n without computing all the terms before it. For a geometric sequence, the explicit formula is a(n) = a(1) · r^(n−1).": "明确的公式可以直接从位置编号 n 中找到任何术语,而不计算它面前的所有术语。对于几何序列,明确的公式是 a(n) = a(1) ° r(n-1) 。",
  "What is a recursive formula?": "什么是递归公式?",
  "A formula that defines each term using the previous term, such as a(n) = r · a(n−1)": "使用上一个术语定义每个术语的公式,例如 a(n) = r = r  * a(n-1)",
  "A formula for the common ratio": "共同比率公式",
  "A formula that calculates any term directly from n": "从 n 直接计算任何术语的公式",
  "A formula used only in arithmetic sequences": "仅在算术序列中使用的公式",
  "A recursive formula defines each term in relation to the previous term. For geometric sequences, it is a(n) = r · a(n−1), meaning you multiply the previous term by the common ratio to find the next one.": "递归公式 相对于上一个术语来定义每个术语 。 对于几何序列, 它是 a( n) = r / a( n) 1 , 意指您将上一个术语乘以 共同比率 来找到下一个 。",
  "What does it mean for a geometric series to converge?": "几何序列集合意味着什么?",
  "The terms alternate in sign": "签名中的替代术语",
  "The sum of all terms approaches a finite value, which happens when |r| < 1": "所有术语的总和接近一个有限值,当 < 1",
  "The terms get larger without limit": "条件无限制地扩大",
  "The series has exactly 10 terms": "这个系列有十个字,十个字",
  "An infinite geometric series converges (has a finite sum) when the absolute value of the common ratio is less than 1. The sum formula is S = a(1)/(1 − r), and it only works when |r| < 1.": "当共同比率的绝对值小于1时,一个无限的几何序列会(有一定总和)趋同,当共同比率的绝对值小于1时,总和公式是S=a(1)/(1)-(r),只有在 {r} < 1 时才起作用。",
  "What is the difference between an arithmetic and a geometric sequence?": "算术和几何序列之间有什么区别?",
  "They are the same thing": "它们是同一回事",
  "Arithmetic sequences have ratios while geometric sequences have differences": "相对序列具有比率,而几何序列则有差异",
  "Arithmetic sequences add a constant difference; geometric sequences multiply by a constant ratio": "对数序列增加不变差异;几何序列乘以恒定比率",
  "Geometric sequences always increase while arithmetic sequences decrease": "几何序列总是增加,而算术序列则减少",
  "In an arithmetic sequence, you add the same number (common difference d) to get from one term to the next. In a geometric sequence, you multiply by the same number (common ratio r). This fundamental distinction separates the two types.": "在算术序列中,您会添加从一个术语到下一个术语的相同数字(共同差 d)。在几何序列中,您会乘以相同数字(共同比率 r)。这一基本区别将两种类型区分开来。",
  "What is a finite geometric series?": "什么是有限的几何序列?",
  "A geometric sequence where r = 0": "r=0的几何序列",
  "The product of all terms in a sequence": "所有术语的产物按顺序顺序排列",
  "The sum of a fixed number of terms in a geometric sequence": "几何序列中固定数术语之和",
  "A geometric sequence with no end": "无尽尽的几何序列",
  "A finite geometric series is the sum of the first n terms of a geometric sequence. Its formula is S(n) = a(1)(1 − rⁿ)/(1 − r), which adds up a specific number of terms.": "限定的几何序列是几何序列第一个 n 条件的总和。 其公式是 S(n) = a(1)( 1) - rn) /(1 - r), 加上一个具体数目的术语。",
  "What does a negative common ratio produce in a geometric sequence?": "负共同比率在几何序列中产生什么?",
