  "Terms that are all zero": "全部为零的词句",
  "All negative terms": "所有负值",
  "When r is negative, multiplying a positive term by r gives a negative term, and multiplying that negative term by r gives a positive term again. This creates an alternating pattern of positive and negative values.": "当 r 是 负 时, 乘以 正 值乘以 r 表示 负 值, 乘以 r 表示 负 值 表示 负 值 , 乘以 r 表示 负 值 表示 正 值 。 这造成了正 值 和 负值 的交替模式 。",
  "What is the nth term of a geometric sequence?": "几何序列的第n个术语是什么?",
  "The sum of the first n terms": "第一个n学期的总和",
