  "The common ratio raised to the nth power": "与Nnth电源的共同比率提高",
  "The nth term is the specific value at position n in the sequence. It is calculated using the explicit formula a(n) = a(1) · r^(n−1), where a(1) is the first term and r is the common ratio.": "nth 术语是序列中的 n 位置的具体值。 它使用明确的公式 a(n) = a(1) / r(n-1) 计算, 其中 a(1) 是第一个术语, r 是共同比率。",
