  "The sequence doubles each time": "每次顺序都加倍",
  "When r = 1, multiplying any term by 1 gives the same value. So every term equals a(1), creating a constant sequence like 5, 5, 5, 5, ... Technically, geometric sequences typically require r not equal to 1.": "当 r = 1 时, 将任何术语乘以 1 给予相同值。 所以每个术语等于 a (1) , 产生一个恒定序列, 如 5 、 5 、 5 、 5 、 5 、 . . 技术上, 几何序列通常要求 r 不等于 1 。",
  "A chain email starts with 1 person who sends it to 4 others. Each recipient sends it to 4 new people. How many people receive the email in the 5th round of forwarding?": "连锁电子邮件从一个发送到另外四个人的人开始。 每个接收者都发送到4个新人。 第五轮转发中有多少人收到电子邮件?",
