  "A tree grows in a pattern where the number of new branches each year forms the sequence 3, 6, 12, 24, .... How many new branches will appear in year 7?": "一棵树的生长模式是,每年新的树枝数量构成顺序3、6、12、24.。第7年将出现多少新的树枝?",
